original_title: World Series of Fighting 16: Palhares vs. Fitch
overview: World Series of Fighting 16: Palhares vs. Fitch was a mixed martial arts event held December 13, 2014 in Sacramento, California, United States.  WSOF 16 featured two championship title bouts: The main event was a fight for the WSOF Welterweight Championship between champion Rousimar Palhares and challenger Jon Fitch.  The co-main event was a fight for the WSOF Featherweight Championship between champion Rick Glenn and Lance Palmer.
title: World Series of Fighting 16: Palhares vs. Fitch
